data_table.description: Structural Brain Segmentation by MRI Using Freesurfer Software, Offspring Cohort from 2005 - 2010. These include total volume, surface area, gray matter volume, thickness and curvature for the left and right hemispheres. These measures have been assessed by means of two parcellation atlases: Destrieux and Desikan-Killiany.
